remarks: Also misspelling in GrB <Mesosagattia decipiens nid:1029234>.
Possibly to be merged under Sagittidae (Gasmi et al., 2014), and not with Spadellidae as suggested by Papillon et al. (2006) from a mistake in sequences.

Suggested as a synonym of Platidia anomioides in Emig (2012:21). Révision des espèces de brachiopodes décrites par A. RISSO. Carnets de Géologie [Notebooks on Geology] - Article 2012/02 (CG2012_A02): 15-30.
Also misspelling in GrB <Mesosagattia decipiens nid:1029239>.
As Mesoplodon bidens (Sowerby, 1804; nid=180515) in GrB (2014) .  In Frantzis (2009:2), could be one or more of M. densirostris, M. europaeus and possibly M. bidens.
The genus Crania is reserved for fossils.
Symomymy after Emig C.C. (2014).- Novocrania turbinata synonyme de N. anomala.- Carnets de Géologie [Notebooks on Geology], Brest, vol. 14, nº 8, p. 159-171.
